title: 2021 North 1 Region wrestling: Wrestleback semifinal results (Reg. 1 & 2)
body: The best high school boys wrestlers in New Jersey open pursuit of state titles on Saturday with the opening round of the NJSIAA/Rothman Orthopaedics wrestling tournament.The North Jersey, Section 1 Region tournament is set for Mount Olive High School.Complete results are on the way from , so stay tuned.The wrestleback semifinals:6-, Paramus Catholic d. 8-, West Essex, 2-0 (SV).5-, Boonton d. 3-, West Milford, 5-0.2-, High Point md. 8-, Paramus Catholic, 9-1.5-, New Milford d. 7-, Mount Olive, 3-2.3-, Bergen Catholic d. 8-, Pascack Hills, 15-0 (TF 2:53).5-, Montville d. 6-, Lenape Valley, 1-0.3-, Don Bosco Prep p. 9-, Mahwah, 0:52.4-, Newton md. 7-, West Essex, 14-1.Note to readers: if you purchase something through one of our affiliate links we may earn a commission.
